:: Attack On a Beach in Veracruz [Done Breaks] {"position":"961,1392","size":"100,100"}
<<switch $faction>>
<<case "Spaniards">>
Though you have been expecting a visit from the notorious Mexica, you were not prepared for them to launch a surprise attack. Fortunately, you are prepared when a band of warriors bears down upon you at the beach. You have your weapons and your dogs at your side. They have clearly underestimated your strength.<br>
<br>
After a short and ferocious battle, you force the attackers to retreat but it has cost you. You had the greater numbers this time and they were clearly unprepared for your weapons, but you might not be so lucky when you meet again.<br>
<br>
<<if $TL_Attacks is "No">>
