<br>
<br>

<<switch $role>>
<<case "Tlacaelel" or "Cuauhtemoc" or "Cacamatzin" or "Aztec_Priest" or "Pochteca">>
You read Moctezuma's Proclamation, and you gather together in Council, this time without Moctezuma present. <br>
<br>
The arrival of the strangers and mysterious omens have left everybody unsettled. How should you proceed? Does Moctezuma's Proclamation inpsire confidence, or is it time to choose a new leader? In this strange new world, who will you follow?<br>
<br>
<<link "Moctezuma" "Moctezuma Confidence Vote">><<set $MocMut_Moc+=1>><<set $Moc_Mut_Vote+=1>><<set $Moctezuma_Loyalty+=1>><</link>> retains your loyalty, you trust his leadership. <br>
<br>
<<link "Tlacaelel" "Moctezuma Confidence Vote">><<set $MocMut_Tla+=1>><<set $Moc_Mut_Vote+=1>><<set $Tlacaelel_Loyalty+=1>><</link>> has shown great leadership. You vote for him. <br>
