<<link "Cuauhtemoc" "Moctezuma Confidence Vote">><<set $MocMut_Cua+=1>><<set $Moc_Mut_Vote+=1>><<set $Cuauhtemoc_Loyalty+=1>><</link>> is clearly the one to lead you through these strange times. 

<<case "Moctezuma">>
<<if $Moc_Mut_Vote isnot 5>>
You wait, on edge, wondering what the reception of your proclamation will be. You know that your counselors are meeting without you, but about what?<br>
<br>

<<elseif $Moc_Mut_Vote is 5>>
After meeting without you, your counselors call you [[into the chamber|Moctezuma Confidence Vote]].
<</if>>
